title: Hour 3 - Charles Barkley, Justin Herbert
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Charles Barkley, Justin Herbert
description:
Dan chats with TNT NBA Analyst Charles Barkley as the NBA season opens tonight. And he also talks to Los Angeles Chargers QB Justin Herbert about last night's overtime win over the Denver Broncos.
